{"tid":969291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那開抓了！「翻牆」罰比吸毒還重","createTime":"2019-01-05T03:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T09:52:52.000Z","uid":32511,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f56c07c19ae6b688ae88ce027346557ae9f765f7","tid":969291,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"中國廣東韶關南雄市公安局近日對一名「翻牆」的朱姓網友開罰，理由為「擅自建立、使用非法定信道進行國際聯網」，處以罰款人民幣1000元（約新台幣4500元），被發現竟比違法吸毒罰的多一倍，有網友諷刺：「吸毒自取滅亡，翻牆中共滅亡」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpAZ9P2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpAZ9P2q.jpg&h=4567adca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpH2g7zu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpH2g7zu.jpg&h=145ffb1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpPaixDA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpPaixDA.jpg&h=6b0d37bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有另一名重慶市的黃姓網友，近日也因「翻牆」被當地警方傳喚。（圖擷取自推特）<br />\n <br />\n據行政處罰決定書上資訊，這名朱姓網友因自去年8月起，頻繁使用藍燈（lantern pro）軟體進行翻牆上網，被官方查獲開罰。<br />\n <br />\n事件曝光後有網友好奇在「廣東公安執法信息公開平台」網站上查看相關內容，發現另一名違法吸毒的陳姓民眾被處以罰款人民幣500元，竟比翻牆罪行少一倍，讓網友在推特上疑惑表示，「翻牆比吸毒嚴重？」有人則解釋：「吸毒自取滅亡，翻牆中共滅亡。兩權相害取其輕，兩權相利取其重。」<br />\n <br />\n另有網友在推特指出，重慶市近日也有一名翻牆的黃姓網友收到警方傳喚通知，更讓中國網友們人心惶惶，指出「以後每天的翻牆，戰戰兢兢」。"},{"pid":"0e360dbbe55786c559cf04664e2152efee55b62d","tid":969291,"uid":20659,"like":34,"dislike":4,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:03:30.000Z","msg":"支那唯一德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa45c8d74dd232b4c0394cbe0758907138469837","tid":969291,"uid":44454,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:06:21.000Z","msg":"硬係重過吸毒啦，吸毒最多害自己，翻牆係害人"},{"pid":"420cf1d5a1a027728b1b7a5c44ecaf01922c69a9","tid":969291,"uid":42487,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"五毛翻牆會捉嗎"},{"pid":"1e046c0eeae4caf60e4429d7bf27e251b5affbac","tid":969291,"uid":3020,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"420cf1d5a1a027728b1b7a5c44ecaf01922c69a9","tid":969291,"uid":42487,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"五毛翻牆會捉嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"佢地用香港sim唔洗翻牆"},{"pid":"e615f69ecbc40b814ce347d5861dee6b2d2dae2c","tid":969291,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"吸毒可提升GDP"},{"pid":"1393a1e2d26fd0bf8c1fab38434cfb7f46319c71","tid":969291,"uid":186784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:25:44.000Z","msg":"捉得幾多 每分每秒都有芝麻人係到翻牆上fb架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f7f02e7892db69ebb54c302995243a9d190cf5","tid":969291,"uid":83228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"華偉Twitter <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3572f971075d24994778cb834dfe23e0da7999ff","tid":969291,"uid":23180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d3f7f02e7892db69ebb54c302995243a9d190cf5","tid":969291,"uid":83228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"華偉Twitter <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"黨部門唔計"},{"pid":"e6812083d81c699822e004904ab1e3fb5f585087","tid":969291,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1393a1e2d26fd0bf8c1fab38434cfb7f46319c71","tid":969291,"uid":186784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:25:44.000Z","msg":"捉得幾多 每分每秒都有芝麻人係到翻牆上fb架啦<img